The paper discusses alternative communication strategies in the field of High-Energy Physics (HEP), including the use of online repositories and digital libraries. This suggests that cs.DL (Digital Libraries) is a likely sub-category. The analysis of citation data and clickstreams also suggests that cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CY (Computers and Society) may be relevant sub-categories. The paper also touches on issues related to publishing and open access, which could place it in the cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) sub-categories.
